A typical SOC Lab Architecture we build will look like this be low

```
           ┌───────────────┐
           │   Kali Linux  │
           │  (Attacker)   │
           └──────┬────────┘
                  │
           Virtual Network
                  │
        ┌─────────┴─────────┐
        │                   │
┌───────────────┐   ┌───────────────┐
│   Windows 10  │   │    Splunk     │
│  (Victim)     │   │     SIEM      │
│ Splunk Agent  │   │  Log Analysis │
└───────────────┘   └───────────────┘
```

**Roles**

| Machine | Purpose |
| --- | --- |
| Kali Linux | Attack machine |
| Windows 10 | Victim machine generating logs |
| Splunk | Collects & analyzes logs |

